  "Description": "The TestBasicAskOverride goal registers a handler to intercept the default ask channel for user input. It prompts the user to enter their name and stores the input in the variable \\%userName\\%. If the entered name is not 'TestUser', an error is thrown indicating the test has failed. If the name is correct, a success message is displayed.",
